txt.en: 'A fine beast and a fine victory! I never doubted you could do it, of course.'
Linnet is located in the south-central Wildwood.\n\nYou should talk to Linnet Redholm.
In the Wildwood roams an elk with a coat as black as pitch.
Dúgar the Black Elk can be found in the southern Wildwood.\n\nLinnet has asked you to defeat the Black Elk, Dúgar.

'Dúgar the Black Elk. His was one of the first tales to reach my ears. They say he roams the southern Wildwood, fleet of foot and fierce of horn.\n\n'Think you are up to the task of defeating him? Others have tried and failed.'
